 tai nạn ô tô. Không nói với Lolita của định mệnh của mẹ cô, Humbert đưa cô vào một chuyến đi ô tô xuyên quốc gia, nơi mối quan hệ của họ bắt đầu vượt ra ngoài ranh giới truyền thống của cha dượng và con gái riêng ..</p>","tmdb":{"type":"movie","id":"9769","season":null,"vote_average":7.109,"vote_count":1920},"modified":"2024-10-23T11:16:13.000Z","cast":["Jeremy Irons","Dominique Swain","Melanie Griffith","Frank Langella","Suzanne Shepherd","Keith Reddin","Erin J. Dean","Joan Glover","Pat Perkins","Ed Grady","Angela Paton","Michael Goodwin","Ben Silverstone","Emma Griffiths Malin","Ronald Pickup"],"director":["Adrian Lyne"],"cast_meta":[{"name":"Jeremy Irons","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Jeremy Irons","tmdb_id":16940,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/w8Ct1q02Ht3sWdOSqfp3B85TzT.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/16940"},{"name":"Dominique Swain","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Dominique Swain","tmdb_id":11149,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/7zRGmaNRvUCtbD4K3o6Hjmw65IL.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/11149"},{"name":"Melanie Griffith","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Melanie Griffith","tmdb_id":29369,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/yffPcqlZMsXTCAZ84a1tLmdcIS6.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/29369"},{"name":"Frank Langella","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Frank Langella","tmdb_id":8924,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/86DEo3sBguyc1l46606yVKD28T4.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/8924"},{"name":"Suzanne Shepherd","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Suzanne Shepherd","tmdb_id":11484,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/nkfMXeTtkGPPRzvun3mBTntkiOS.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/11484"},{"name":"Keith Reddin","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Keith Reddin","tmdb_id":181299,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/uKbIyBnAYmWjbRUvnRUl46Rpmsy.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/181299"},{"name":"Erin J. Dean","name_vi":null,"n